data.description: Conveniently located with a view you can’t miss out on! Come check out this duplex, full of potential or utilize it as a single family if that's your preference! A front yard, a spacious deck, large driveway with plenty of parking; what’s not to love! Downstairs is a 2 bedroom/1 bathroom with a full kitchen for potential rental income while upstairs is 2 bed/2 bath with access to the deck. You can also enjoy bonus space located at the back of the house for shop use, hobbies, green house, etc. Minutes away from schools, grocery stores, and Carlanna Lake trail for hiking.
